---
layout: null
permalink: /articles.json
---
{% comment %}
This JSON feed powers the dynamic article cards on the homepage and blog page.
Weekly workflow:
1. Add a new markdown file inside `_posts/`.
2. Optionally add `description:` in the post front matter.
3. The count, latest articles section, and blog list update automatically.
{% endcomment %}
[
{% for post in site.posts %}
  {
    "title": {{ post.title | jsonify }},
    "date": {{ post.date | date: site.date_format | jsonify }},
    "description": {{ post.description | default: post.excerpt | strip_html | strip_newlines | truncate: 180 | jsonify }},
    "link": {{ post.url | relative_url | jsonify }},
    "isoDate": {{ post.date | date_to_xmlschema | jsonify }}
  }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
{% endfor %}
]
